data.description: OPEN HOUSE 1/21/2024 11 a.m. - 2 p.m.!  Come view this completely renovated 3 bedroom & 1 bathroom home on a quiet street that includes a large driveway suitable for multiple cars! All windows & doors are hurricane impact proof & energy efficient. New roof, AC, fence & tankless water heater within the last 6 years, and full remodel completed within the last 2 years! This home includes a water purifying system that alkalizes the water both inside & outside and has a backyard with a shed that has additional living space. This one will go fast!
